{
  "stem": "2004.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I just can't understand that they lived so long, and they lived through the war, and somehow, they couldn't resist it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they just, just couldn't resist the butter, and the fat, and the bacon, and whatever else they had there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, they were warned-- we were-- this was something which was repeatedly warned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Loudspeakers warned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Signs warned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They personally came across the prisoners, actually the former inmates, and they were warned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They says, eat bread and hard-boiled eggs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Stay away from fat because this is poison for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm not so careful now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not-- I'm not even careful now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I eat more than I should, fat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's a different situation now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, you're talking about not having any, any fat of any kind for three years, and then all of a sudden, you start eating this thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you see, we were-- they were in a run-down condition, and this contributed to them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, after being liberated three weeks later, or four weeks later, the Jewish Brigade from Palestine, which was part of the English Army, arrived at Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, young people, whoever wants to go to Palestine, which was at that time Palestine, please join us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We will take you to Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as soon as there's an opportune time, you will all immigrate to, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So many, many of us went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They transported us to Italy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And partially by truck, partially by train, we ended up in the southernmost part of Italy-- the heel of the boot-- the famous heel of Italy.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, I must point out another thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
